[07:37] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'that users have to sign in basically in order to reach that dashboard." So, now after a few seconds, it\'s created its to-do list. It needs to install Clerk, obviously. It\'s going to set up our local environment variables. It\'s going'

[07:50] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'to move through the entire thing, and then from there, we should be good to actually test that sign-up. Okay, so now that this thing is done, if we were to go and try to just access that dashboard that we accessed before, we can see'

[08:02] [scene:talk]
