AUDIO: 'easily. So, if we were to just go down and say user management and profiles, it\'s now going to run that entire process through again and give us a new skill that helps us, in this case, with the next stage of the process, which is user management and profiles. And so,'

[09:22] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'now just like earlier, we have detailed documentation on how to actually use, in this case, like the user data properly inside of our app. So, if we were using server components, this is how we could'

